          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Half-Staff for Homeland Heroes Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires that the U.S. flag be flown at half-staff in honor of a member of the Armed Forces who dies from an injury incurred or aggravated while serving on active duty in the United States. </p>]]></text>
